'''碧昂斯马蝇'''（学名：''Scaptia beyonceae''）是一种在[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]][[昆士兰州|昆士兰州]]北部发现的一种罕见的[[马蝇|马蝇]]，于1981年在[[凯恩斯_(昆士兰州)|凯恩斯]]以西的[[阿瑟顿台地|阿瑟顿台地]]采集，<ref>{{cite web| language =en| publisher =ABC| title =CSIRO unveils bootylicious Beyonce fly| url =http://www.abc.net.au/news/2012-01-13/horse-fly-named-after-beyonce/3771224| date =2012-01-13| accessdate =2012-01-18| archive-date =2012-01-17| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20120117182651/http://www.abc.net.au/news/2012-01-13/horse-fly-named-after-beyonce/3771224| dead-url =no}}</ref>，这种马蝇因尾部有漂亮的金黄色绒毛，故澳大利亚科学家布赖恩·莱萨德以[[美国|美国]]歌星[[碧昂丝·诺利斯|碧昂丝·诺利斯]]命名这一物种。<ref>{{cite web| language =zh| publisher =南方报业网| title =生物学家用碧昂斯命名马蝇 因拥有“漂亮的臀部”| url =http://nf.nfdaily.cn/nfdsb/content/2012-01/18/content_36632401.htm| date =2012-01-18| accessdate =2012-01-18| deadurl =yes| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20120118045200/http://nf.nfdaily.cn/nfdsb/content/2012-01/18/content_36632401.htm| archivedate =2012-01-18}}</ref>

